Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time it takes for SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to occur after SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average duration of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation until the next activity (SW-Awaiting EIC Decision)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total elapsed time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that include both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation, conditioned on at least one SW-Reviewer Agreed occurring in between
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time between the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed and the start of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation within the same case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases where multiple reviewer agreements (SW-Reviewer Agreed) preceded it
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer No Response and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation when both appear in the same trace
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases that originated from an initial rejection path
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time between the final SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in complex reviewer assignment variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers Challenge Paper to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation when SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs at least once in between
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers Challenge Paper' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time from the first SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants involving repeated reviewer invitations
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in traces containing Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 or 2
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
